name: Black Bird Cards
description:
3 cards with a black bird each in a different design. (if you want to see each design email me I can send you a jpg of each)
All are blank inside so you can write and wish whatever your heart desires!
Each card comes with a matching envelope with a little version of the bird printed right on the front of the envelope!
Each card is 5×7.

name: "Truthseeker" Letterpress
description:
Do you seek the truth? Then you are a truthseeker who thinks out of the box!
Three flat note cards in three different colors, sea green, powder blue, chartreuse . Comes with 3 envelopes with chartreuse square on back flap. These are printed letterpress on a C&P new style press. This is a very simple design with a stong message! It is my favorite design I have done.

name: Letterpress Love you "squared" (or 2)
description: Fun card for all occasions!! It is always nice to tell someone that you love them (squared or 2). Powder blue and red letterpress on white card stock. letterpress was done on a vandercook press.

name: WHAT THE... Letterpress flat card
description: 5 FLAT CARDS WITH THE WORDS WHAT THE… PRINTED ON THE FRONT. 5X7 chipboard with red letterpressed woodblock type, hand pressed by me on a C&P press. Use the cards as a post card or when a driver cuts you off you can hold it up to them and let them now how you feel. “WHAT THE…” CAN BE FOLLOWED WITH ANY FUN,COLORFUL,OR EXPICIT WORD YOU CAN THINK OF! You fill in the blank when choosing who to give it to or mail too! Have fun with it all my cards come in a clear sleeve tied with ribbon.
